<P>And fir&s;t, the country is rare for its <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> al&s;o <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> from &s;tone, well wa<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ered, well <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> quantity of inter|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> miles in length and bredth without <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> abundance of m<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">berry trees in &s;ome parts of it, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> apple <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> before General Sullivan's ar|my <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> down, and greatly abounded with peach <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span">, hazle-nuts and black wa<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="4 letters"> ma<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">y <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> afording a plenty of fi&s;h, &s;alt <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> where I <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">de &s;ome &s;alt, a &s;ort of root with <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> made bread, they call it <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">okt<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">haw, a <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> plenty of wild mandrakes.</P>
